name: Shopnet Network
description: The namespace itself - Level 0 contains the entire SND system

name: Thing
description: Discoverable entities that humans or agents can find
examples: iPhone, domain name, article, consulting service

name: Location
description: Physical places on or above Earth (lat/long)
notes: NEW - physical world equivalent to sn_

name: Transaction (Non-Financial)
examples: Email sent, package shipped, receipt issued

name: List
description: Collections of UIDs or things owned by users

name: User
description: Identity - persons or entities that own data

name: Agent
description: Software agents under user direction (First Law)

name: CloudFront On-Demand
description: Lambda-backed site that scales to zero

name: Layer3 Web3
description: Lambda@Edge with IP certs for emoji TLDs

name: User Device
description: End-user client devices (phones, tablets, laptops, desktops, watches, TVs)
examples: iPhone, Android phone, MacBook, Windows PC
notes: Added Feb 9, 2026 - Moved from Infrastructure. Pulse method: none (pending client app)

name: Apple iOS
notes: iOS devices require Apple Developer account

name: Google Android
notes: Android devices use Google Play Services

name: Smartwatch
examples: Samsung Galaxy Watch, Wear OS watch

name: Product
description: Physical or digital goods for sale

name: Information
examples: How to bake bread article, dataset

name: Message
description: Communication sent from one party to another

name: Items
examples: JSONB array of UIDs or refs
